Getting Started

Prerequisites

· Rust 1.75+
· Node.js 18+
· Solana CLI 1.18+ (for on‑chain operations)
· Docker (for daemon builds)

Build All

```bash
make build
# compiles Rust SDK, WASM, TypeScript, and mobile bindings
```

Run the Off‑Chain Daemon

```bash
cd daemon
cargo run --release
# listens on localhost, performs async device checks
```

Use the SDK

```typescript
import { DeviceTrustClient } from '@gitdigital/zk-device-trust-mask';

const client = new DeviceTrustClient();
const riskScore = await client.evaluateDevice();
const proof = await client.generateAttestation();
// submit to on‑chain program or verify via daemon
```

